    },
    {
        "role": "bullet_intro",
        "segment": "Guidelines for selecting a reusable component include:",
        "citations": [
            {
                "type": "source_text",
                "content": "If you are a consumer for your current project, there are four key characteristics to check about the components you are about to reuse:",
                "img_id": null
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "role": "bullet",
        "segment": "Does the component perform the function or provide the data you need?",
        "citations": [
            {
                "type": "source_text",
                "content": "- Does the component perform the function or provide the data you need?",
                "img_id": null
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "role": "bullet",
        "segment": "If minor modification is required, is it less modification than building the component from scratch?",
        "citations": [
            {
                "type": "source_text",
                "content": "- If minor modification is required, is it less modification than building the component from scratch?",
                "img_id": null
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "role": "bullet",
        "segment": "Is the component well-documented, so you can understand it without verifying its implementation line by line?",
        "citations": [
            {
                "type": "source_text",
                "content": "- Is the component well-documented, so you can understand it without having to verify its implementation line by line?",
                "img_id": null
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "role": "bullet",
        "segment": "Is there a complete record of the component's test and revision history, so you can be certain it contains no faults?",
        "citations": [
            {
                "type": "source_text",
                "content": "- Is there a complete record of the component's test and revision history, so you can be certain that it contains no faults?",
                "img_id": null
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "role": "paragraph",
        "segment": "Additionally, consumers must assess the amount of code needed to interface their system with the reused components.",
        "citations": [
            {
                "type": "source_text",
                "content": "You must also assess the amount of code you need to write so that your system can interface with the reused components.",
                "img_id": null
