                "content": "Schum distinguishes five categories of evidence: Tangible evidence, Testimonial evidence, Equivocal testimonial evidence, Missing evidence, Accepted facts.",
                "img_id": null
            }
        ],
        "type": null
    },
    {
        "role": "bullet",
        "segment": "Tangible evidence: objects, documents, demonstrations, models, maps, charts.",
        "citations": [
