        "citations": [
            {
                "type": "source_text",
                "content": "Testimonial evidence: This type of evidence is supplied by another person, who can tell us how the evidence was obtained. Schum distinguishes three kinds of testimonial evidence: direct observation, second-hand, and opinion.",
