    {
        "role": "paragraph",
        "segment": "The relative errors for the projects are: A: |8060 - 8000| / 8000 = 0.0075, B: |9000 - 10000| / 10000 = 0.10, C: |7000 - 7200| / 7200 = 0.0278, D: |15000 - 13000| / 13000 = 0.1538, E: |10000 - 9600| / 9600 = 0.0417.",
        "citations": []
    },
    {
        "role": "paragraph",
        "segment": "The MMRE is the mean of these values: (0.0075 + 0.10 + 0.0278 + 0.1538 + 0.0417) / 5 = 0.06616, which rounds to 0.07.",
        "citations": []
    },
    {
        "role": "sentence",
        "segment": "Therefore, the MMRE for Jenna's estimating technique is 0.07.",
        "citations": []
    }
]

