        "citations": [
            {
                "type": "source_text",
                "content": "Risk management involves several important steps, each of which is illustrated in Figure 3.15. First, we assess the risks on a project, so that we understand what may occur during the course of development or maintenance. The assessment consists of three activities: identifying the risks, analyzing them, and assigning priorities to each of them.",
