    {
        "role": "paragraph",
        "segment": "To calculate PRED(.25), we count how many estimates are within 25% of the actual value and divide by the total number of projects.",
        "citations": []
    },
    {
        "role": "paragraph",
        "segment": "For each project, the relative error is calculated as |Estimate - Actual| / Actual:",
        "citations": []
    },
    {
        "role": "bullet_intro",
        "segment": "Relative errors for each project are:",
        "citations": []
    },
    {
        "role": "bullet",
        "segment": "Project A: |5000 - 10000| / 10000 = 0.5 (50%)",
        "citations": []
    },
    {
        "role": "bullet",
        "segment": "Project B: |25000 - 20000| / 20000 = 0.25 (25%)",
        "citations": []
    },
    {
        "role": "bullet",
        "segment": "Project C: |50000 - 80000| / 80000 = 0.375 (37.5%)",
        "citations": []
    },
    {
        "role": "bullet",
        "segment": "Project D: |70000 - 110000| / 110000 = 0.3636 (36.36%)",
        "citations": []
    },
    {
        "role": "bullet",
        "segment": "Project E: |40000 - 45000| / 45000 = 0.1111 (11.11%)",
        "citations": []
    },
    {
        "role": "bullet",
        "segment": "Project F: |45000 - 50000| / 50000 = 0.1 (10%)",
        "citations": []
    },
    {
        "role": "paragraph",
        "segment": "Counting the projects with relative error less than or equal to 0.25 (25%): Projects B, E, and F meet this criterion.",
        "citations": []
    },
    {
        "role": "paragraph",
        "segment": "Therefore, 3 out of 6 projects are within 25% of the actual value, so PRED(.25) = 3/6 = 0.5.",
        "citations": []
    },
    {
        "role": "paragraph",
        "segment": "The correct answer is d. 0.50.",
        "citations": []
    }
]

