[
    {
        "role": "paragraph",
        "segment": "The conceptual design will be useful for communicating with the representative of the consolidating organization; it may contain financial jargon but not implementation details or programming jargon.",
        "citations": [
            {
                "type": "source_text",
                "content": "In preceding chapters, you examined requirements for the Loan Arranger, and devised several designs to implement your solution to the described problem.",
                "img_id": null
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "role": "sentence",
        "segment": "The conceptual design will not include detailed financial formulas so it will be independent of the implementation.",
        "citations": [
            {
                "type": "source_text",
                "content": "It is early in the development process of the Loan Arranger system for FCO. You do not yet have a comprehensive set of requirements for the system. All you have is an overview of system functionality, and a sense of how the system will be used to support FCO's business.",
                "img_id": null
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "role": "sentence",
        "segment": "The technical design should contain more detail about what data structures will need to be used in order to meet the performance requirements.",
        "citations": [
